name: Heal
description: Heal allows patients to search for and explore doctors based on their specialty, location, availability, and reviews. Patients can then reserve an appointment with their chosen doctor at a convenient time and date. The app provides a user-friendly interface that simplifies the process of finding and booking a doctor's appointment.

name: Vestique
description: Vestique is a clothing web app that offers a wide range of chic and trendy clothing options for women. From casual wear to formal dresses, Vestique has something for every occasion. With a user-friendly interface and easy navigation, shopping for the latest fashion trends has never been easier. Browse through their collection and find the perfect outfit to suit your style and personality. Stay up to date with the latest fashion trends and make a style statement with Vestique.
